18_7	0.0	Grand jury proceedings are normally secret.
18_8	0.0	Hiss' son, Tony, praised the judge's ruling, saying his father hoped ``the full truth would be disclosed and people could see for themselves that he had always been an honorable and patriotic public servant''.
